text: Krasny Klyuch () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Krasnoklyuchevsky Selsoviet, Nurimanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 2,274 as of 2010. There are 30 streets. == Geography == It is located 30 km from Krasnaya Gorka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Nurimanovsky District
title: Krasny Klyuch, Nurimanovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
